title: Hi, I'm Sebastian.
textcustomer: I'm a passionate developer with a keen interest in continuously learning and applying new technologies to my projects. I pay close attention to detail and am highly receptive to client and user feedback, striving to provide the best experience possible. I am adaptable and work well in team environments, whether it involves front-end development or diving into back-end tasks. When faced with challenges, I seek assistance from colleagues or consult documentation to find solutions. I am excited to join a dynamic team where I can contribute to and grow with the company's innovative projects.
